item.title: Crazy Animals: The Rescue
item.description: Help the "Crazy Animals" from this flooding, they must cross dangerous path to reach the safety of the boat. Go through these paths using 15 different objects and obstacles in 21 funny levels.
item.instruction: Mouse click to play, and "R" to restart.

item.title: Zombie Rumble
item.description: Zombies took over your town, and you as a respectable citizen who have to protect your home. It's time to kill all zombies!
item.instruction: Arrow keys to move and Spacebar to shoot.

item.title: Saving Maria
item.description: Play through all 30 levels of this physics platformer in the hope that you can go to the exit and save Maria.
item.instruction: Use arrow keys to move.

item.title: Athos Vs Beasts
item.description: This is a physics based shooting puzzle game. Trow the bombs at evil beasts to destroy them. There are 30 base levels, 4 chapters (Church, Town, Bastion, Castle) , 3 special levels (blowing tubes) and 9 types of throwing objects (bombs, spears, stones), enjoy!
item.instruction: mouse left click to throw objects, R to replay.

item.title: Moony Cat
item.description: This is a funny casual puzzle game. Swap objects so the cat can eat moon and bring the sunrise. These levels are not that simple as it seems to be!
item.instruction: mouse left click to play.

item.title: Horde Attack
item.description: Zombies are inside the compound, eliminate them, Quickly!
item.instruction: Spacebar to continue / pause, WASD to move and mouse left click to shoot.
item.tags: shooting, shoot, shooter, guns, zombie, attack

item.title: The Time Warrior
item.description: To prove he is the greatest warrior of all time, Asthor will travel through time to defeat all of these Warriors. A fast paced beat em up with superb StickMan animations. Over 40 weapons and dozen of enemies.
item.instruction: WASD or arrow keys to move, mouse click to attack.
item.tags: stickman, beat, fighting, battle, action, fatality, bloody

item.title: Bumper Boat Fighter
item.description: Become the best of 3 matches, bump your opponents out.
item.instruction: Use arrow keys to move, spacebar to do a special attack.

item.title: 3D Moto Racing

item.title: Ragdoll Truck
item.description: Your mission is to drive a few rookies to the camp. It's ok to throw and smash them, you can even drop them or run them over. The only point is to bring someone alive!
item.instruction: left arrow: turn left, right arrow: turn right, up arrow: forward, down arrow: stop, backward. press "R" to restart

item.title: Ben 10's Zombie Survival

item.instruction: S: pick up weapon or bottles, Left and Right arrow keys: move, Spacebar: hit or shoot, Enter: release the big skill when the rage is full.
